{
  "stem": "8775.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, in 1948, the Communist regime took over in Hungary from the coalition government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Communists, even though they were atheist, you know, they didn't believe in the religion, but they didn't tolerate anything against Jews or anything against minorities.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I didn't hear too much about it, except when I was up in the university.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they found out about my Zionistic background.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's why when I finished my university with high honors, they did not consider me as a good so-called candidate for a top position, because they don't trust my political instincts or--",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those being the heads of the party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The heads of the party.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, like all these universities were pretty much controlled by--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the functionaries of the Communist party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So if you were not a Communist party member, no matter how good a student you were or how well you knew your stuff, it didn't help.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were delegated to lower type positions in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They discriminated against you, not because you were Jewish, but just simply because you were not a member of the elite, which was the party, the people affiliated with the Communist party.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I graduated in 1949, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, I'm going way back in 1949.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after I graduated in 1954, we had several years we can really celebrate. 1953 I got married with my lovely wife.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name is Mary, or Maria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are married 42 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in 1954, I graduated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In 1955, my daughter was born.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we moved to Gyor, where my mother lived with her husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in 1956, we came over to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The revolution started.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came out to the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
